s politburo would ease its monetary policy stance to accommodate more easing. That comes following fiscal stimulus measures that were</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151863095/image_2151863095.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743363-gxc-etf-china-stocks-soar-after-bullish-monetary-policy-news", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 21:10:53"}, {"id": "4743374", "title": "The U.S. 10yr Heads Back To 4%, But Then It's 5%+ For 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bond market, trading screen with a falling chart of a 10 year US bond, symbolic for rising yields.\" data-id=\"1367313345\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"947px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367313345/image_1367313345.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p 