hot of Oilfield Worker Using Digital Tablet next to Oil Pump Jack\" data-id=\"2156728724\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">halbergman/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>On November 5, U.S. voters had an energy policy choice. The outgoing administration supported addressing climate change by continuing the U.S. energy policy to support alternative and renewable fuels and inhibiting the production and consumption of hydrocarbons. The incoming administration</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743355-oih-pros-and-cons-of-oil-services-etf-product", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:41:47"}, {"id": "4743352", "title": "Bitcoin ETFs Showdown: Is BITU Worth The Volatility?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract Bitcoin Cryptocurrency concept\" data-id=\"1368998806\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Olemedia</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of my \u201cBitcoin ETFs Showdown\u201d series, where I analyze several Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) ETFs and compare them to the iShares Bitcoin Trust ETF (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBIT\" title=\"iShares Bitcoin Trust ETF\">IBIT</a>).</p> <p>Today, I will analyze for the first time a leveraged Bitcoin ETF: the ProShares Ultra</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743352-bitcoin-etfs-showdown-bitu-worth-volatility", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:34:02"}, {"id": "4743349", "title": "EVG: Not An Attractive Entry Point Anymore For This CEF (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fixed income concept. Types of investment security that pay investors fixed interest or dividend payments until their maturity date. Finance business conceptual. Money bag.\" data-id=\"1625101509\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"910px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p cla